column4: Love to let others share the spotlight.
column5: 我喜愛讓他人分享聚光燈。

column4: Love to make other people happy.
Make certain that my plans will work.
column5: 我確保我的計劃會成功。

column4: Make decisions only after I have all of the facts.
column5: 我只在掌握所有事實後才做決定。

column4: Must try to maintain harmony within my group.
column5: 我必須努力維持團體內的和諧。

column4: Only get what I want because I work hard for it.
column5: 我只因為努力工作才得到我想要的。
我更喜歡獨自做每件事。

column4: Prefer to participate fully rather than view life from the sidelines.
column5: 我更喜歡充分參與，而不是從旁觀者的角度看待生活。

column4: Read a large variety of books.
column5: 我閱讀各種各樣的書籍。

column4: Refuse to take credit for work I haven't done.
column5: 我拒絕為我沒有做過的工作邀功。
儘管面臨挑戰，我仍保持希望。

column4: Speak up in protest when I hear someone say mean things.
column5: 當我聽到有人說刻薄的話時，我會站出來抗議。
我停下來數算自己的祝福。

column4: Support my teammates or fellow group members.
column5: 我支持我的隊友或團體成員。

column4: Take pride in not exaggerating who or what I am.
column5: 我為自己不誇大自己是誰或是什麼感到自豪。

column4: Tend to think of alternatives when someone tells me how to do something.
column5: 當有人告訴我如何做某事時，我傾向於想出替代方案。

column4: Think about what is good in my life when I feel down.
column5: 當我感到沮喪時，我會想到生活中美好的事物。

column4: Think that my life is extremely interesting.
column5: 我認為我的生活極其有趣。

column4: Treat others differently if I don't like them.
column5: 如果我不喜歡他人，我會以不同方式對待他們。

column4: Try not to do favors for others.
column5: 我試圖不為他人做好事。

column4: Try to add some humor to whatever I do.
column5: 我試圖在我做的任何事情中加入一些幽默。

column4: Try to have fun in all kinds of situations.
column5: 我試圖在各種情況下玩得開心。

column4: Try to have good reasons for my important decisions.
column5: 我試圖為重要決定找出充分的理由。

column4: Try to identify the reasons for my actions.
column5: 我試圖找出我行動的理由。

column4: Try to make my group members happy.
column5: 我試圖讓團體成員快樂。

column4: Try to make sure everyone in a group feels included.
column5: 我試圖確保團體中的每個人都感到被包容。

column4: Try to respond with understanding when someone treats me badly.
column5: 當有人對我不好時，我試圖以理解回應。

column4: Try to tease my friends out of their gloomy moods.
column5: 我試圖用取笑讓朋友擺脫陰暗的心情。

column4: Use laughter to brighten the days of others.
column5: 我用笑聲照亮他人的日子。

column4: Weigh the pro's and the con's.
Will succeed with the goals I set for myself.
column5: 我會在為自己設定的目標上取得成功。

column4: Work best when I am alone.
Would never be described as arrogant.
column5: 我永遠不會被形容為傲慢。
